cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NA, cs.MM 

The paper deals with linear dimensionality reduction techniques for image analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses nonnegative matrix factorization (NMF), which is a popular machine learning technique (cs.LG) and involves optimization algorithms (cs.NA). The paper proposes a new variant of NMF that incorporates spatial information, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and image processing (cs.MM).
